### List all currencies
GET http://localhost:3000/api/currencies

### Get currency by ID (USD)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/currencies/1

### Get currency by ID (EUR)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/currencies/2

### Get currency by ID (GBP)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/currencies/3

### Get currency by code (USD)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/currencies/code/USD

### Get currency by code (lowercase - should work)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/currencies/code/eur

### Get non-existent currency by ID (should return 404)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/currencies/999

### Get non-existent currency by code (should return 404)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/currencies/code/XYZ

### Get live exchange rates for base currency (USD)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/currencies/rates/USD

### Get live exchange rates for base currency (EUR)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/currencies/rates/EUR
